{
  "stem": "13469.7",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "By that time, the, the war had finished, and Germany had been divided up into Russian, American, British, French zones.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And we wanted to go back to Holland.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And, and the first step to get there was to get to the American zone.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "The Russians laid down transport for us and quite a number of others who wanted to go back to Holland.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And we were taken to Leipzig, which was in the American zone.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was very interesting that we'd forgotten all about Eve.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We-- well, as I'll explain in a minute, kind of thing-- we, we'd had our own problems on the train, foraging with food.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we did sort of in the back of our minds know that she was with the Birnbaums at the orphanage.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, and we did know that she was on the train, and we presumed that they were looking after themselves.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we hadn't really seen her at all.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then, you know, the, the first couple days of liberation, we were busy.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then we had typhus for two weeks in a Russian hospital, far away from Trebitz.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So we hadn't-- that's our excuse that we hadn't the opportunity to see her.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And when we came back to Trebitz, we-- I don't know what happened, whether we were blanked out, or whether we were still in bad condition, but we just forgot about Eve.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And this is very bad to say, but--",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we were taken to Leipzig, together with a lot of other people who wanted to go back to Holland, Belgium, France, et cetera, anything where we all had to go to the American zone.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there, we had the first bit of sort of processing, really.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
